
note over browser:
user provides a value for the input and clicks send 
end note
note over browser:
Client stores user input data on a notes array and calls a re-render
end note
browser --> server : HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa


note over server: 
server adds the request body content to existing notes and confirms operation with 201
end note
server-->browser: response status 201 created 